description.value: The workload field represents the total amount of work (in duration) associated with a Task. It's used in aggregate workload computation for Resource Planning. You can configure this System Calculated Field but the "Output Format" must be of type "Duration". Default formula = {duration}.
If this field is empty, the Task Template is visible in all Projects. If the field is populated, the template is only visible in the linked Projects.
